{% extends 'front/base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Bienvenue - AGRI GO{% endblock %}

{% block stylesheets %}
    {{ parent() }}
    <style>
        body {
            background: #efefef;
        }

        .front-nav {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6ece3;
            backdrop-filter: none;
        }

        .front-nav .nav-link,
        .front-nav .navbar-brand {
            color: #1f5d37;
        }

        .front-nav .nav-link:hover {
            color: #144728;
        }

        .front-hero {
            display: none;
        }

        .front-shell {
            background: transparent;
            border: 0;
            box-shadow: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .home-hero {
            min-height: 78vh;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            background:
                linear-gradient(rgba(17, 24, 18, 0.52), rgba(17, 24, 18, 0.52)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523741543316-beb7fc7023d8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80') center/cover;
        }

        .hero-inner {
            width: min(980px, 92vw);
            animation: rise 0.8s ease;
        }

        .hero-kicker {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.6px;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            opacity: 0.92;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            line-height: 1.04;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.7vw, 1.2rem);
            max-width: 72ch;
            margin: 0.85rem auto 0;
            color: rgba(248, 251, 247, 0.92);
        }

        .section-light {
            width: min(1260px, 94vw);
            margin: 3rem auto;
        }

        .section-eyebrow {
            color: #1d7a4b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
            color: #1d2f24;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .problem-grid {
            margin-top: 1.6rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .problem-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #d9ded6;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(37, 62, 40, 0.08);
        }

        .problem-card h3 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
            color: #1f3627;
        }

        .problem-card p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #516356;
        }

        .split-feature {
            margin-top: 3.1rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            min-height: 520px;
        }

        .split-image {
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500937386664-56d1dfef3854?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') center/cover;
        }

        .split-content {
            background: #0f6a35;
            color: #edf7ef;
            padding: clamp(1.2rem, 2.8vw, 2.4rem);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .split-content h3 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.7vw, 2.5rem);
            line-height: 1.08;
            margin-top: 0.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        }

        .split-content p {
            color: rgba(230, 246, 235, 0.9);
            max-width: 50ch;
        }

        .split-content ul {
            margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
            padding-left: 1.1rem;
        }

        .split-content li {
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        }

        .modules {
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .modules-grid {
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 0.9rem;
        }

        .module-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dce4da;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            min-height: 220px;
        }

        .module-index {
            color: #97a49c;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
        }

        .module-card h4 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            color: #1d3024;
            margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
        }

        .module-card p {
            color: #4b5f51;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .vision-panel {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dce4da;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .vision-panel h3 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            color: #193a2a;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .vision-panel p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #47594d;
        }

        .newsletter {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            background: #ececec;
            border-top: 1px solid #d9dfd6;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dfd6;
            padding: 1.8rem 0;
        }

        .newsletter-inner {
            width: min(1260px, 94vw);
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .newsletter h4 {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            margin: 0;
            color: #1b2f44;
            font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.95rem);
        }

        .newsletter p {
            margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
            color: #65706a;
        }

        .newsletter input {
            border: 1px solid #0f6a35;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 0.65rem;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #45614f;
        }

        .site-footer {
            background: #0a0d12;
            color: #d5dbd4;
            padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
        }

        .footer-inner {
            width: min(1260px, 94vw);
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.3fr repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        .footer-title {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .footer-inner ul {
            padding-left: 0;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-inner li {
            margin-bottom: 0.32rem;
            color: #c1cbc1;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            width: min(1260px, 94vw);
            margin: 1rem auto 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #20252f;
            padding-top: 0.85rem;
            color: #97a497;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        @keyframes rise {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(16px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1200px) {
            .modules-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .problem-grid,
            .split-feature,
            .modules-grid,
            .newsletter-inner,
            .footer-inner {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .newsletter input {
                margin-top: 0.45rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="home-hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="hero-kicker">AGRI GO - Tunisia 2026</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Smart Agricultural Management Platform Built For Tunisia</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">AGRI GO modernizes agriculture by replacing manual and paper-based processes with an integrated digital ecosystem. The mission is simple: deliver practical, local, and accessible digital tools for real farming operations.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-light">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">The Problem & Market Need</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Tunisian agriculture needs a local digital shift</h2>
    <div class="problem-grid">
        <article class="problem-card">
            <h3>Efficiency losses</h3>
            <p>Current manual practices still produce major losses, including around 30% yield loss and 40% water wastage due to delayed field decisions.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="problem-card">
            <h3>Operational hurdles</h3>
            <p>Farmers face fragmented land management, rising irrigation costs, and repeated human errors caused by paper notes and disconnected spreadsheets.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="problem-card">
            <h3>Solution gap</h3>
            <p>Available products are often expensive, weak in predictive capability, and not sufficiently adapted to Tunisian climate and local operations.</p>
        </article>
    </div>

    <div class="split-feature">
        <div class="split-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="split-content">
            <p class="section-eyebrow" style="text-align:left;color:#9ed4b2;">Proposed Solution</p>
            <h3>Smart + Local + Accessible agriculture platform</h3>
            <p>AGRI GO is designed for Tunisia 2026 with one clear objective: modernize farm operations through connected modules that improve productivity while reducing resource waste.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Target impact: +25% productivity and -35% water usage</li>
                <li>Field workflows adapted to fragmented farms and local constraints</li>
                <li>From planning to harvest in one continuous ecosystem</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="modules">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Platform Architecture</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Five interconnected modules</h2>
        <div class="modules-grid">
            <article class="module-card">
                <div class="module-index">01</div>
                <h4>Cultures & Parcelles</h4>
                <p>Interactive mapping, weather-context actions, and automated alerts for disease or water stress.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="module-card">
                <div class="module-index">02</div>
                <h4>Smart Irrigation</h4>
                <p>Automatic irrigation piloting that triggers when soil humidity drops below 30%.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="module-card">
                <div class="module-index">03</div>
                <h4>Predictive Stocks</h4>
                <p>Intelligent purchase recommendations to optimize inventory and reduce resource waste.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="module-card">
                <div class="module-index">04</div>
                <h4>Workforce Management</h4>
                <p>Task planning and GPS check-ins for workers via a dedicated mobile workflow.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="module-card">
                <div class="module-index">05</div>
                <h4>Harvests & Sales</h4>
                <p>Automatic document generation and crop lifecycle tracking from harvest to sales follow-up.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="vision-panel">
        <h3>Project Vision</h3>
        <p>AGRI GO transforms agriculture from manual management into a data-driven operational model that is understandable, affordable, and adapted to Tunisian realities. It is built to answer concrete field challenges with measurable impact, not just to digitize forms.</p>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="newsletter">
    <div class="newsletter-inner">
        <div>
            <h4>Follow AGRI GO Evolution</h4>
            <p>Stay connected to project updates, module demos, deployment milestones, and agriculture-focused improvements.</p>
        </div>
        <input type="text" value="Newsletter contact: agrigo.team@project.local" readonly aria-label="newsletter-contact">
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
        <div>
            <h3 class="footer-title">AGRI GO</h3>
            <p>Smart Agricultural Management Platform tailored for Tunisian agriculture in 2026.</p>
            <p><strong>Positioning:</strong> Smart + Local + Accessible</p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> agrigo.team@project.local</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h4 class="footer-title">Useful Links</h4>
            <ul><li>Home</li><li>Cultures</li><li>Parcelles</li><li>Administration</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h4 class="footer-title">Core Modules</h4>
            <ul><li>Cultures & Parcelles</li><li>Smart Irrigation</li><li>Predictive Stocks</li><li>Workforce</li><li>Harvests & Sales</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h4 class="footer-title">Field Challenges</h4>
            <ul><li>Yield Losses</li><li>Water Wastage</li><li>Fragmented Land</li><li>Manual Errors</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h4 class="footer-title">Expected Impact</h4>
            <ul><li>+25% Yield</li><li>-35% Water Use</li><li>Faster Decisions</li><li>Integrated Management</li></ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">Copyright AGRI GO. Built as a practical digital response to Tunisian agriculture challenges.</div>
</footer>
{% endblock %}
